Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan silent over Falklands
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wvmt
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 May 1982
President Reagan leaves Haig to talk about US policy over the Falklands. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less